Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.29,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san.}Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.25,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Are you thinking about \Nour assignment from earlier?}Cậu đang nghĩ về tiết học lúc nãy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.24,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Assignment?}Tiết học?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.47,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's not what it's about.}Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.72,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{My maid is the only thing I think about all day.}Tớ chỉ toàn nghĩ về hầu gái của mình thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.17,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I just realized it, and now \NI don't know what to do.}Nên khi nhận ra thì thấy khó xử.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:29.08,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Would you please tell me more about that?}Cậu có thể nói rõ hơn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.88,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I might be able to help\N you with your troubles.}Tớ có thể sẽ giúp gì được đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.33,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Well, then...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:41.81,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Ever since Lilith first came to the mansion,}Từ ngày Lilith đến dinh thự,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:44.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{she's made me both curious and suspicious.}cô ấy vô cùng khó hiểu và đáng ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.81,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can't take my eyes off her.}Tớ không thể rời mắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Every time I think about her, \Nmy heart races.}Mỗi lần nghĩ về cô ta là tim tớ lại rộn ràng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:58.24,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{My chest gets tight,}Ngực thắt lại,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{and I can't sit stil—}và không thể ngồi yên--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.11,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't know what to—}Tớ không biết phải làm sao--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.73,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wait, are you okay?!}Khoan, cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.83,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Don't mind me.}Đừng để ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.62,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{This happens all the time.}Chuyện thường ngày thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.93,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{All the time?}Thường ngày?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's even more worrying.}Vậy thì càng đáng lo đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:20.22,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Well, then, how does she \Nseem to you, as a person?}Vậy cậu thấy chị ấy là người thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.98,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's just really suspicious.}Vô cùng đáng ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.85,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Suspicious?}Đáng ngờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:29.29,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She showed up at my mansion one \Nday and started working for free.}Cô ta xuất hiện vào ngày đó và bắt đầu làm việc miễn phí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Her sparkling purple eyes are so pretty,}Tròng mắt màu tím quyến rũ,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:35.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{and the way she works so hard is beautiful.}và dáng vẻ làm việc chăm chỉ vô cùng xinh đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:39.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Just being near her makes me happy.}Chỉ cần lại gần là tớ cũng thấy vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Everything about Lilith is suspicious.}Tất cả mọi thứ về Lilith đều đáng ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.29,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-What's wrong?}C-Chuyện gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.02,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's not really suspicious\N so much as... well...}Tớ không nghĩ nó đáng ngờ đâu, đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.07,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's definitely love.}Chắc chắn là tình yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:56.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, also!}Cả cái đó nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:00.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{The meals she makes are extra delicious.}Bữa ăn cô ta làm rất ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:04.09,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And she smells especially nice.}Và mùi của Lilith cũng thơm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's way too suspicious!}Quá đáng ngờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.72,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It's even more intense \Nthan in the stories I read.}Nghe chính chủ kể chuyện còn tuyệt hơn\N tự tưởng tượng nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:17.65,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Thank you! Thank you!}Cảm ơn! Cảm ơn ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:20.85,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.18,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{So what is it that's troubling you?}Vậy cậu lo lắng điều gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.08,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{When Lilith smiles, I feel happy, too.}Khi Lilith cười, tớ thấy hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{When Lilith looks sad, I feel sad.}Khi Lilith buồn, tớ cũng buồn theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:37.53,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{When Lilith is talking to someone else,\N I can't contain myself.}Khi Lilith nói chuyện với người khác, tớ không thể kìm chế.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith is my maid...}Lilith là hầu gái của tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.95,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's so suspicious...}Cô ta rất đáng ngờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And yet it's like my mind isn't my own.}Trái tim này cứ như không phải của tớ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't get it.}Tớ không hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:52.44,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She's so suspicious, \Nyet I don't ever want to leave her.}Mặc dù rất đáng ngờ nhưng lại không muốn rời xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm so confused.}Tớ vô cùng bối rối.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.05,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Ever since I met her,\N I've become more and more messed up.}Từ ngày gặp cô ta thì tớ dần trở nên kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I might be...}Có lẽ tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.34,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It might be that...}Không có lẽ tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:08.52,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm sick.}Tớ bị bệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Whenever I ask her, \Nshe just dodges my question.}Dù có hỏi thì Lilith cũng chỉ né tránh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:17.11,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I think I'm seriously ill,\Nand she just won't tell me!}Tớ nghĩ mình bị bệnh mà cô ta lại giấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:22.70,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Isn't that the nature of your relationship?}Quan hệ của hai người không phải là thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.73,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What is our relationship?}Quan hệ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.99,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{W-Wait a moment... Have you been \Noblivious this whole time?}K-Khoan đã... Cậu không nhận ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.73,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I thought this was just humble bragging!}Tớ cứ nghĩ cậu đang khoe khoang chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Bragging?}Khoe khoang?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.29,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Never mind...}Không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:41.72,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Anyway, I'm really messed up.\N I can't deal with this.}Tóm lại tớ đang rất kì lạ. Thật khó khăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.04,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't know what to do.}Tớ không biết phải làm gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{How do I fix this confusion syndrome?}Làm sao để chữa căn bệnh này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:52.11,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Even now, it's hard to breathe \Nwhen I think about Lilith.}Ngay cả lúc này khi nghĩ về cô ta là ngực tớ thắt lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{If you—}Nếu cậu--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.09,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san.}Yuuri nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:59.78,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{What you're feeling isn't an illness.}Cảm xúc đó không phải bệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.89,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I've read about it in a book.}Tớ đã đọc về nó trong sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:05.71,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It's more painful and \Nagonizing than being sick,}Nó đau đớn và đau khổ hơn bị bệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:08.62,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{but you want to treasure it just the same.}Nhưng cậu lại muốn nâng niu nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.47,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{You're...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.80,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{in love.}tình yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.81,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Love?}Tình yêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:26.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Love...}Tình yêu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.94,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What is love?}Tình là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.81,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I-I'm home.}T-Tôi về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, young master.}Chào mừng chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.93,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're home quite late today.}Hôm nay ngài về hơi muộn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:47.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You always come home early, \Nso I was very lonely.}Ngày nào ngài cũng về sớm nên tôi có hơi cô đơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kidding.}Đùa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.51,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{H-Huh?}H-Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.25,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:59.69,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I thought we had grown closer recently...}Cứ tưởng gần đây thân nhau hơn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.26,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{One more try.}Lần nữa nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:05.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The weather is getting cooler.}Trời đã trở nên lạnh hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You don't feel chilled, do you?}Ngài có thấy lạnh chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:12.45,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Shall I warm you up?}Hay để tôi sưởi ấm cho?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{With my bare skin?}Với làn da nâu ngon nghẻ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kidding.}Đùa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.54,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He would normally say...}Bình thường sẽ phản ứng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:26.99,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I wasn't cold at all. Thinking about \Nyou made my chest feel warm!}Tôi không có lạnh! Nghĩ về cô là đủ làm cơ thể ấm áp rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.74,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{...something like that in response.}...đại loại vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.83,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Why is he so unresponsive?}Sao hôm nay lại bình thản đến thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.89,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There have been times when he wasn't \Nsuspicious of me in the past, but why...}Ngài ấy đã luôn nghi ngờ mình từ lúc mới đến mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.26,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{H-He hasn't come to hate me, has he?}K-Không lẽ mình bị ghét?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:44.18,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{N-No, it's too early to assume that.}K-Không! Còn sớm để kết luận.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.53,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Maybe he simply didn't hear me.}Có khi ngài ấy không nghe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.83,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That must be it.}Chắc chắn là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.98,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Let's try again.}Thử lại nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.02,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Will you have dinner?}Ngài có ăn tối không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Or will you have a bath?}Hay muốn tắm trước?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:59.39,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Or will you have... me?}Hay là ăn tôi trước?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kidding.}Đùa thôi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.34,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That might have been going too far!}Hình như mình làm hơi quá rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.32,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Th-That wasn't...}C-Chuyện vừa rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.90,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-I didn't mean anything by it!}T-Tôi không có ý gì đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.03,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This isn't good.}Không ổn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.88,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Y-Y-Young master!}C-C-Chủ nhân!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:24.10,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you feeling ill in some way?}Ngài bị bệnh sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.13,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you hurt? Do you have a fever?}Đau ở đâu? Có sốt không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Nothing like that.}Không phải thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.09,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What's the matter?}Có chuyện gì mà hỏi vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's the matter?}Chuyện gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.32,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Well, you...}Thì ngài...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.07,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{...aren't reacting to me.}...không có phản ứng với tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:41.90,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Wait, that makes it sound \Nlike I'm some crazy maid!}Khoan, nghe thế khác gì mình là loại hầu gái đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:48.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-It's just that you seem unwell.}T-Tôi thấy ngài có vẻ không khoẻ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was just thinking about something.}Tôi chỉ đang suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.73,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry to worry you.}Xin lỗi vì làm cô lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:02.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No, I apologize for scampering around.}Không ạ, tôi cũng xin lỗi vì hơi nham nhở.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.35,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{By the way, what is it\N you've been thinking about?}Vậy ngài đang suy nghĩ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Well...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.17,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{L...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Y?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.47,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's a secret for now.}Hiện tại là bí mật.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.41,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{You don't understand love?}Cậu không hiểu tình yêu là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:28.06,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I tried reading books and stuff,}Tớ đã thử đọc qua sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:32.37,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{but there's nothing that \Nexplains my feelings for Lilith.}Nhưng chẳng có cuốn nào giải thích cảm xúc\N của tớ cho Lilith cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:36.44,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{In that case, why don't we \Ndiscuss it more at my place?}Vậy thì sao chúng ta không thảo luận về nó nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:40.31,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I'll show you what love is.}Tớ sẽ cho cậu thấy tình yêu là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:45.08,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Welcome, Yuuri-san.}Chào mừng cậu Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.07,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thank you for having me.}Cảm ơn vì đã mời.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.89,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Please bring some tea \Nto the terrace in the yard.}Hãy chuẩn bị trà ở sân.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.11,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:57.82,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Mother, this is my friend from school.}Mẹ ơi, bạn của con nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.39,Main,Tsukasa's Mom,0,0,0,,{Oh, my. Welcome.}Ôi chà, chào mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.48,Main,Tsukasa's Mom,0,0,0,,{Please make yourself at home.}Cứ tự nhiên như ở nhà nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yes, ma'am.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:09.50,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't like this kind of atmosphere.}Mình không thích bầu không khí này lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.34,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It reminds me of the past.}Nó làm mình nhớ lại ngày xưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.40,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith told me to bring this.}Lilith nói tớ nên mang theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.46,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{My!}Chà chà!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.08,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,Bánh hạnh nhân!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.72,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Thank you!}Cảm ơn cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.83,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I love financiers.}Tớ thích lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.30,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I sure can count on your maid.}Không hổ danh là hầu gái của Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.49,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Why don't we have them together?}Chúng ta ăn cùng nhau nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.73,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Let's eat.}Chúc ngon miệng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.46,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Delicious!}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.44,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith made them herself.}Lilith tự làm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:55.84,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{So your maid is good at making sweets, too.}Hầu gái của cậu làm được cả đồ ngọt sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:56.85,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She is.}Được.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.77,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith's cooking is the best in the world.}Tài nấu nướng của Lilith là số 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:09.51,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{By the way, couldn't your maid come today?}Cơ mà hôm nay hầu gái nhà cậu không đi cùng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.35,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{You should have come together.}Đáng ra phải đến cùng nhau chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:16.05,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She brought me part of the way, \Nbut I sent her home.}Có đi theo đến giữa đường nhưng về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.04,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Shall we invite her now?}Hay giờ gọi chị ấy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:21.14,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I can have someone fetch her.}Tớ sẽ kêu người đến đón.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Uh... But...}Hả? Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:34.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith might decide to leave \Nmy mansion and work here.}Lilith có thể sẽ muốn rời nhà tớ và qua đây làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:41.78,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{A kind family, lots of servants, \Na large, beautiful mansion...}Một gia đình tốt bụng, nhiều gia nhân, dinh thự to đẹp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:45.73,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{All the things I lost are abundant here.}Tất cả những thứ tớ đánh mất đều ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:51.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She'd make a lot more money \Nworking for your family.}Nếu làm việc cho cậu sẽ kiếm được rất nhiều tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:55.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{She might be much happier \Nhere than living with me.}Cô ấy có thể sẽ vui hơn khi ở cùng tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.06,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san...}Yuuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.41,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Never mind being in l\ove.}Chưa bàn tới tình yêu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:07.52,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't know if I can even\N give her happiness.}Mình còn không biết bản thân có làm Lilith thấy vui không.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:12.18,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I can't imagine your maid\N would think that.}Tớ không nghĩ chị ấy sẽ làm ở đây đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:20.20,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{She looked very happy being with you.}Vì chị ấy rất hạnh phúc khi bên cạnh cậu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.42,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Do you really think so?}Cậu nghĩ thế thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.79,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.47,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I see...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.51,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Có chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:37.98,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Oh, nothing.}À không.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:42.26,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Anyway, we were talking about \Nwhat love is, weren't we?}Mà chúng ta đến đây bàn về tình yêu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:49.62,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{In that case, you should read \Nmy collection of romance novels.}Vậy thì hãy đọc qua bộ sưu tập tiểu thuyết lãng mạn của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.11,sign_18201_195_Love_Romance,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,184)}{Love Romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.11,sign_18201_196_Emerald_s_First_,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,184)}{Emerald's First Love}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.11,sign_18201_197_Lovesick_in_Love,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,184)}{Lovesick in Love}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.11,sign_18201_198_The_Darkness_and,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,184)}{The Darkness and Light of Passion}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.19,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Young lady...}Tiểu thư...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.35,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{You can't take these \Noutside without permission.}Lại mua mà chưa được cho phép sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.41,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{The master will scold you again.}Chủ nhân sẽ la mắng nữa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.78,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.17,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Just for a bit!}Một chút thôi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.28,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I just need to borrow them for a bit!}Tôi chỉ mượn chút thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.97,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:09.35,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I still never figured out what love is.}Cuối cùng mình vẫn chưa biết tình là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:11.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm home.}Tôi về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.36,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, young master.}Mừng ngài đã về, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.84,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's the matter?}Có chuyện gì sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:28.09,Flashback - Sus Maid,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{She looked very happy.}Chị ấy trông có vẻ rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.41,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's nothing.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.97,Main,Sensei 2,0,0,0,,{The art contest is coming up.}Sắp đến cuộc thi vẽ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:44.95,Main,Sensei 2,0,0,0,,{You'll be drawing pieces to submit.}Các em sẽ vẽ một bức tranh và nộp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.69,Main,Student 3,0,0,0,,{What should we draw?}Vẽ gì thì được ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.04,Main,Sensei 2,0,0,0,,{Anything you'd like.}Bất cứ gì các em thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.17,Main,Sensei 2,0,0,0,,{What's important is that you \Nobserve what you draw carefully.}Quan trọng là phải quan sát thật cẩn thận rồi mới vẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:58.77,Main,Sensei 2,0,0,0,,{That way, no matter what you draw, you'll begin to see its true nature.}Làm thế thì dù có vẽ gì các em cũng sẽ\N nhìn ra được bản chất thực sự của nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.15,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{True nature...}Bản chất...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.33,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's it!}Chính là nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.67,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You'd like to draw me?}Ngài muốn vẽ tôi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:09.64,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{By drawing Lilith,\N I'll expose her true nature.}Bằng cách vẽ Lilith, \Nmình sẽ nhìn ra bản chất thực sự của cô ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's for a school assignment.}Cho bài tập trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.98,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{May I draw you?}Tôi vẽ được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.48,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, of course.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:18.14,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Và mình cũng chưa biết tình yêu là gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:23.76,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Look at me very carefully \Nand draw me thoroughly.}Hãy nhìn tôi thật kĩ từ đầu đến chân và vẽ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kidding.}Đùa thôi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.20,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Got it!}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.33,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{All right, here I go.}Vẽ thôi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:35.93,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You have...}Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.02,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{two moles under your eye,}có hai nốt ruồi dưới mắt,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.35,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{and one on your chest.}một cái ở ngực.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:41.97,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.43,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:46.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{N-Nothing.}K-Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:49.03,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can't draw you if you hide your face.}Giấu mặt thế thì sao mà vẽ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.91,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You were the one who said \Nto observe you thoroughly.}Cô là người nói tôi phải quan sát thật kĩ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.56,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's right! I have to pose!}Phải rời, tôi sẽ tạo dáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:02.55,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Wouldn't it be better if you \Ndrew me taking a proper pose?}Sẽ dễ hơn nếu tôi tạo dáng cho ngài vẽ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's true.}Đúng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.19,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And my clothes.}Và cả quần áo nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.75,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{If you're going to draw me,\N I should be dressed properly.}Nếu định vẽ thì tôi phải ăn mặc chỉn chu lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.40,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.10,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,N-Ngài muốn tôi trông thế nào ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll let you see me how ever you'd like.}Bất cứ gì ngài thích tôi sẽ chiều theo cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How about this kind of pose?}Thế này thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.38,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Or this kind of pose?}Hay thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.67,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{want to draw you just as you are.}muốn vẽ cô thật trần trụi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.72,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,T-Trần trụi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{D-Do you mean...}T-Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:32.85,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.00,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just as I am...}Trần trụi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:45.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The way I always am?}Ý ngài là tôi lúc bình thường?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.04,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's the Lilith I always see.}Lilith mà tôi hay thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The way you see me}Cách chủ nhân thấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:16:00.45,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{and the way you think of me\N isn't necessarily who I really am.}và nghĩ về tôi không hẳn là tôi thực sự đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:05.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I might look completely different \Nwhen you don't see me.}Khi ngài không nhìn tôi thì tôi \Nsẽ là con người khác hẳn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{R-Really?}T-Thật sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:08.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's suspicious.}Đáng ngờ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:16.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But no matter how you look, I'll find you.}Nhưng dù cô trông thế nào thì tôi cũng sẽ tìm ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're you.}Cô là cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:24.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Besides, there's no one as suspicious as you are.}Với cả làm gì có ai đáng ngờ hơn cô đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.33,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That should do it.}Thế này nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{May I take a look?}Tôi có thể xem qua không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.45,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're very good.}Ngài vẽ giỏi quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.09,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I never knew you had a talent for art, too.}Tôi chưa từng biết ngài có tài hội hoạ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:44.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.72,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No!}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.72,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're much more beautiful than this!}Cô còn xinh đẹp hơn thế này!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What? I think it looks beautiful.}Hả? Nhưng tôi nghĩ nó đủ đẹp rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.35,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, no!}Không được!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:54.34,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're a lot more sensual. \NYou look nothing like this!}Cô gợi cảm hơn nhiều, không thể tầm thường vậy được.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.95,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can't express it with my abilities.}Tôi không thể diễn đạt được bằng khả năng của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:16:59.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.08,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm drawing you more.}Tôi sẽ vẽ lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.53,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Don't move, Lilith!}Đừng di chuyển nhé, Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.53,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'll draw until I'm satisfied!}Tôi sẽ vẽ đến khi nào hài lòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, you have bags under your eyes.}Chủ nhân, mắt ngài thâm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm still not done with my drawing.}Tôi vẫn chưa vẽ xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:21.85,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My...}Chà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:25.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is it because I'm so beautiful \Nthat you can't draw me?}Vì tôi quá xinh đẹp nên ngài không thể vẽ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.75,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Đùa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:33.27,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I think I lost sleep thinking about you.}Tôi mất ngủ vì nghĩ đến cô không đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.19,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh, no...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{H-How much sleep have you lost?}N-Ngài mất ngủ cỡ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.92,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't know.}Tôi không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:43.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was thinking about how to draw \Nyou the whole time I was in bed.}Tôi nghĩ về cách vẽ suốt trên giường.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:45.44,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Before I knew it, it was morning.}Rồi trời sáng lúc nào không hay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.57,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:53.95,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'll take responsibility tonight \Nand put you to sleep.}Đêm nay tôi sẽ nhận trách nhiệm và dỗ ngài ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:02.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How about some healing scents \Nto give you a good night's rest?}Ngài hãy dùng nến thơm để dễ ngủ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.66,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That does smell nice,}Đúng là thơm thật,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.14,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{but you smell nicer.}nhưng cô thơm hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{D-Do I?}T-Tôi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:11.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:16.90,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{In that case, would you like\N to place your head on my lap?}Ngài hãy gối lên đùi tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{If you like my scent, \Nthat may help you sleep better.}Nếu thích mùi của tôi thì như thế sẽ dễ ngủ hơn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.30,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Your legs will go numb.}Chân cô sẽ tê mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.54,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'll be too worried to sleep.}Tôi lo quá và không thể ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.16,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I see...}Vậy sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.79,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How about some hot milk?}Vậy thì sữa nóng?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.75,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Healing music.}Nhạc nhẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{A hot eye-mask.}Bịt mắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.17,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can't sleep.}Không thể ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Then...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:54.71,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Nếu tôi ngủ cạnh ngài thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.93,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kidding.}Đùa thôi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:03.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to sleep with you.}Tôi muốn ngủ cùng cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I think I can sleep if you're with me.}Nếu cô ngủ cùng, tôi sẽ ngủ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{B-But I'm a maid...}N-Nhưng tôi là hầu gái...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.47,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No?}Không được?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Do you think you can fall\N asleep now, young master?}Ngài có ngủ được chưa, chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't know.}Tôi không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:27.91,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why are you at this mansion?}Tại sao cô lại đến dinh thự này?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.97,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to learn more about you.}Tôi muốn biết thêm về cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:38.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I think about you so much \Nall day that I can't sleep.}Nghĩ về cô nhiều quá nên không ngủ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:46.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But even though you're so close to me now,\N you won't tell me about yourself.}Nhưng dù đang ở cạnh bên, \Ncô lại không nói về bản thân cho tôi nghe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There's so much I don't know \Nabout you. It scares me.}Còn quá nhiều điều tôi không biết. Sợ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.57,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm always worried.}Tôi đã luôn lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.80,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's all right, young master.}Không sao cả, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:08.28,Top Italics,Song,0,0,0,,{I want to spend the coming}Em muốn bên cạnh anh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:14.93,Top Italics,Song,0,0,0,,{future alongside you}trong tương lai đó
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.91,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What was this song again?}Bài hát gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:23.25,Top Italics,Song,0,0,0,,{I search to keep shining}Em đi tìm kiếm ánh sáng
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.60,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah...}Phải rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.60,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's the lullaby my mom used to sing for me.}Là bài hát ru mẹ hay hát...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:33.95,Top Italics,Song,0,0,0,,{And walk on down the path}Và bước đi trên con đường
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.93,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{My mom, and...}Mẹ mình và...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.38,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Who was it again?}Ai nữa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.68,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What was it?}Đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.77,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Goodnight.}Chúc ngủ ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.26,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I slept really well!}Tôi đã ngủ rất ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.21,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks to you, Lilith!}Nhờ có cô đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:52.17,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Although it was your fault I couldn't sleep.}Cứ tưởng tại cô mà tôi không ngủ được!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Good morning. I'm glad to hear that.}Chào buổi sáng, thật tuyệt khi nghe nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:59.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's the matter?}Sao vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can't remember what happened\N right before I fell asleep.}Tôi không nhớ được chuyện xảy ra lúc trước khi ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.79,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I remember feeling really nostalgic, but...}Nhưng có một cảm giác rất hoài niệm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Do you remember, Lilith?}Cô có nhớ không Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:09.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Well...}Tôi không biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I wonder.}Chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There you go, dodging my question again!}Lại né tránh câu hỏi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's your fault I couldn't sleep!}Là tại cô mà tôi mất ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:22.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:25.22,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What if I can't fall asleep again?!}Nhỡ tôi lại mất ngủ thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:31.05,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to have you sleep with me \Nagain today after I finish the drawing.}Tôi sẽ ngủ với cô đến khi nào vẽ xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:38.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{B-But then I'll be the one \Nwho ends up sleep-deprived.}N-Nhưng như vậy... tôi sẽ mất ngủ mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.10,Main,Sensei 2,0,0,0,,{A round of applause for Yuuri-kun.}Hãy cho Yuuri một tràng pháo tay nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.71,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The drawing that the young \Nmaster worked so hard on}Chủ nhân đã cố gắng hết sức để vẽ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:55.07,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{went on to win an award in the competition.}và giành chiến thắng cuộc thi.
